You only liked it
when I was taking it?

800
00:55:16,704 --> 00:55:18,576
You don't like it
when I dish it?

801
00:55:18,706 --> 00:55:20,360
I don't like it
either way.

802
00:55:20,491 --> 00:55:22,580
I'm the kind of friend
who's not afraid
to tell you so.

803
00:55:22,710 --> 00:55:24,321
How many of those
do you have left?

804
00:55:37,812 --> 00:55:40,989
Well, I like the green.

805
00:55:41,120 --> 00:55:44,471
Mrs. Helmsley,
they go with your eyes.

806
00:55:44,602 --> 00:55:46,560
[ Laughs ]

807
00:55:46,691 --> 00:55:48,475
Well, the bracelet
is nice.

808
00:55:48,606 --> 00:55:50,956
Yes, this is
our finest set.

809
00:55:51,086 --> 00:55:52,653
But the earrings
are too small.

810
00:55:52,784 --> 00:55:55,439
- Do you have
something larger?
- Larger.

811
00:55:55,569 --> 00:55:57,049
- <i>[ Intercom buzzes ]</i>
- Secretary: <i>Excuse me,</i><i>
Mrs. Helmsley?</i>

812
00:55:57,179 --> 00:55:59,791
I told you I did not
want to be disturbed.

813
00:55:59,921 --> 00:56:01,836
<i>But Mrs. Helmsley,</i><i>
it's about your son.</i>

814
00:56:01,967 --> 00:56:04,491
I don't care
what it's about.
One more interruption

815
00:56:04,622 --> 00:56:07,364
- and you're outta here.
