00:56:12,847 --> 00:56:15,067
She sends her best,

819
00:56:15,197 --> 00:56:16,808
whatever that is.

820
00:56:16,938 --> 00:56:20,377
And your aunt Sylvia
is sending brownies.

821
00:56:20,507 --> 00:56:22,640
You know her answer
to everything is sugar.

822
00:56:26,731 --> 00:56:28,733
You could have
prepared me,
you know.

823
00:56:28,863 --> 00:56:32,389
I didn't plan on this.

824
00:56:32,519 --> 00:56:35,653
I'm talking about
those people out there.

825
00:56:35,783 --> 00:56:37,655
You got a new wife,
you got new kids.

826
00:56:37,785 --> 00:56:40,135
You haven't spoken
to me in three years.

827
00:56:40,266 --> 00:56:41,528
I don't know why.

828
00:56:41,659 --> 00:56:43,400
Jay...

829
00:56:46,664 --> 00:56:49,406
We need to be more close.

830
00:56:49,536 --> 00:56:52,800
In a few weeks,
when you're feeling better,

831
00:56:52,931 --> 00:56:56,151
I'm gonna talk
to Harry about you
coming to work for US.

832
00:57:00,939 --> 00:57:04,551
You'd look younger
with a toupee.

833
00:57:15,388 --> 00:57:18,391
So, what do you
want me to do about it?

834
00:57:18,522 --> 00:57:21,612
Make Jay president
of deco incorporated.

835
00:57:21,742 --> 00:57:23,657
- What?!
- He'll stay in Orlando.

836
00:57:23,788 --> 00:57:25,616
You don't even
have to see him.

837
00:57:25,746 --> 00:57:27,661
[ Chuckles ]
Lee...

838
00:57:27,792 --> 00:57:30,751
Deco does all the purchasing
for the hotels.

839
00:57:30,882 --> 00:57:32,623
Jay can do that.

840
00:57:32,753 --> 00:57:34,451
How can he do that?

841
00:57:34,581 --> 00:57:36,757
He's had no experience
with that sort of thing.

842
00:57:36,888 --> 00:57:40,848
Harry, you like
being seen with me?

843
00:57:40,979 --> 00:57:44,330
You like the way
you feel with me?

844
00:57:44,461 --> 00:57:45,853
I am no dried-up
little quaker

845
00:57:45,984 --> 00:57:48,639
sitting on my ass
knitting doilies.

846
00:57:48,769 --> 00:57:51,424
