953
01:04:30,736 --> 01:04:34,000
Your son is ripping
off your husband,
Mrs. Helmsley.

954
01:04:35,393 --> 01:04:38,875
<i>The Helmsley corporation</i><i>
is being double-billed,</i>

955
01:04:39,005 --> 01:04:41,660
<i>sometimes triple-billed</i><i>
for furnishings</i>

956
01:04:41,790 --> 01:04:44,228
