the difference.

961
01:04:57,328 --> 01:04:59,330
<i>Now I understand</i>

962
01:04:59,460 --> 01:05:01,767
<i>he's in daily</i><i>
contact with you.</i>

963
01:05:01,898 --> 01:05:04,161
Of course he is.
He's my son.

964
01:05:06,424 --> 01:05:08,426
Well, I'll
look into it.

965
01:05:08,556 --> 01:05:11,385
- That'll be all.
- <i>All right.</i>

966
01:05:11,516 --> 01:05:15,041
Oh, have you told
Harry about this yet?

967
01:05:15,172 --> 01:05:16,869
Not yet.

968
01:05:17,000 --> 01:05:19,176
Don't bother.
I'll tell him myself.

969
01:05:23,484 --> 01:05:25,617
Oh, and Stanley...

970
01:05:25,747 --> 01:05:27,271
Yes?

971
01:05:27,401 --> 01:05:29,926
