that to my staff?

1012
01:07:19,513 --> 01:07:21,602
You've had three
heart attacks.

1013
01:07:21,733 --> 01:07:23,996
Tell them that your
stepfather is concerned
about your health

1014
01:07:24,127 --> 01:07:25,824
and sent someone down
to help you out.

1015
01:07:25,954 --> 01:07:27,913
And Leona,

1016
01:07:28,044 --> 01:07:31,308
I'm rehiring Stanley
permanently.

1017
01:07:34,441 --> 01:07:37,227
Now get this straight,
both of you:

1018
01:07:39,011 --> 01:07:41,318
Just one more time,

1019
01:07:41,448 --> 01:07:43,929
one more thing
like this,

1020
01:07:44,060 --> 01:07:46,845
and you're both
out on your asses!

1021
01:07:46,975 --> 01:07:49,195
Oh!

1022
01:07:57,638 --> 01:08:00,424
I apologize for interrupting
your honeymoon, Mimi.

1023
01:08:00,554 --> 01:08:02,861
I wish you
both happiness.

1024
01:08:02,991 --> 01:08:05,211
Thank you.

1025
