I am a very
determined person.

1027
01:08:27,451 --> 01:08:29,366
And I determined long ago

1028
01:08:29,496 --> 01:08:32,238
that I was gonna marry
a man so powerful

1029
01:08:36,112 --> 01:08:38,114
that just by
being his wife,

1030
01:08:38,244 --> 01:08:40,768
