an anonymous manager,
Mrs. Helmsley.

1045
01:10:08,508 --> 01:10:10,031
Absolutely.

1046
01:10:10,162 --> 01:10:11,903
You are
this hotel.

1047
01:10:12,033 --> 01:10:13,557
