1081
01:11:32,853 --> 01:11:35,073
all featuring
the same headline

1082
01:11:35,203 --> 01:11:37,162
with your picture
under it:

1083
01:11:37,293 --> 01:11:40,557
"The only palace
in the world

1084
01:11:40,687 --> 01:11:43,603
