serve wet lettuce.

1099
01:12:35,655 --> 01:12:37,701
Not in my hotels.

1100
01:12:37,831 --> 01:12:40,399
You are lucky
I do not fire every
damn one of you.

1101
01:12:40,530 --> 01:12:43,446
Now get the hell out.
Go on, out out out.
Go on, Mark.

1102
01:12:43,576 --> 01:12:45,186
