1106
01:13:03,291 --> 01:13:04,858
Something I want
to show you.

1107
01:13:04,989 --> 01:13:07,600
See this?

1108
01:13:07,731 --> 01:13:09,428
Pictures
of the royal family.

1109
01:13:10,821 --> 01:13:12,518
That's what I want.

1110
01:13:12,649 --> 01:13:15,391
<i>My picture on 52 cards.</i>

1111
01:13:15,521 --> 01:13:19,395
We can sell
them for mementos
at the hotel.

1112
01:13:21,353 --> 01:13:23,399
What do you think?

1113
01:13:29,448 --> 01:13:31,711
Well, I think it's
a terrific idea.

1114
