my first real house.

1183
01:18:50,464 --> 01:18:52,249
<i>It has trees</i><i>
and a big lawn</i>

1184
01:18:52,379 --> 01:18:55,208
<i>and it only costs</i><i>
$11 million.</i>

1185
01:18:55,339 --> 01:18:57,167
Harry: <i>
$11 million?!</i>

1186
01:18:57,297 --> 01:19:00,300
Leona: <i>
Furnished, Harry.</i><i>
Furnished!</i>

1187
