to the business, right?

1191
01:19:11,355 --> 01:19:13,923
I mean, after all,
we are the business,
aren't we?

1192
01:19:14,053 --> 01:19:16,055
The I.R.S. Can't object.

1193
01:19:16,186 --> 01:19:19,058
